modules.description: This module implements arithmetic operations and type-safe manipulations for typed ordered fuzzy numbers (OFNs), supporting addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division through infix operators. It works with OFNs represented as records containing type family tags (trapezoidal, Gaussian, exponential) and parameter tuples. Functions include type checking, membership evaluation, and conversion between OFN families, with safety checks to prevent improper operations across mismatched types or improper OFNs.
